{
  "2377250": {
    "name": "Whimel Academy",
    "steam_appid": 2377250,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/37cce050448c76fd1bf35d4638bdfdf0.avif?t=1763846019\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras_big/37cce050448c76fd1bf35d4638bdfdf0.webp?t=1763846019 width=1560 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >威梅尔学院是一款节奏舒缓的时间管理游戏，故事发生在一所专为女巫、巫师和初学魔法者打造的奇幻学府。你将探索校园，参加草药学和魔药制作等课程，结识新朋友，或许还能邂逅一段浪漫情缘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/b78e1c1fc08033c343aac9bca85af0a5.poster.avif?t=1763846019\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/b78e1c1fc08033c343aac9bca85af0a5.webm?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/b78e1c1fc08033c343aac9bca85af0a5.mp4?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/e02e7b54119b06135d06a34f45250903.avif?t=1763846019\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras_big/e02e7b54119b06135d06a34f45250903.webp?t=1763846019 width=1560 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >课外活动依然是惠梅尔学院生活中不可或缺的一部分。你可以在校园内寻找兼职工作来赚取金钱，并提升不同专长的属性点。在图书馆整理书籍、在花园中培育新植物，或是在天文塔进行研究，都能帮助你赚取学院活动所需的资金。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的工资可以用来在食堂换取甜点、在市区购入新书，或者为宿舍添置装饰品，比如唱片机和炼金锅。如果你有特别的专长——例如魔药制作或绘画——不妨尝试出售你的作品来资助未来的项目。不过在工作时，也要注意自己的体力；需要时，你可以回到宿舍休息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/204bbdedb80c233d73c5ea07645ac136.poster.avif?t=1763846019\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/204bbdedb80c233d73c5ea07645ac136.webm?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/204bbdedb80c233d73c5ea07645ac136.mp4?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/36afb2db0a478d6f415b2a3286130399.avif?t=1763846019\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras_big/36afb2db0a478d6f415b2a3286130399.webp?t=1763846019 width=1560 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你逐渐适应校园生活，不妨结识身边的同学。游戏中形形色色的角色们——他们各有独特的兴趣与个性——都期待与你相遇。通过互动提升友谊值，你将获得更多深入交流的机会。在威梅尔学院，终生挚友与青春恋情正等待着你来发现！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/049982e43f71de2d08440dc30f465142.poster.avif?t=1763846019\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/049982e43f71de2d08440dc30f465142.webm?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/049982e43f71de2d08440dc30f465142.mp4?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/608b42d2ee67ceca53fece3880f101eb.avif?t=1763846019\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras_big/608b42d2ee67ceca53fece3880f101eb.webp?t=1763846019 width=1560 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以自由装饰自己的虚拟形象、房间以及心爱的猫咪。尽情收集装饰物品，展现你独特的品味与个性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/c332974ed87d5c2d9ab2c281b8e327a0.poster.avif?t=1763846019\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/c332974ed87d5c2d9ab2c281b8e327a0.webm?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/c332974ed87d5c2d9ab2c281b8e327a0.mp4?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于这个充满迷人细节、温馨氛围与生活片段的梦幻世界，玩家仿佛置身魔法国度。踏入这个世界，就像回到半梦半醒间记忆中的童年故居。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/b3461cecee9bb60fa4f1133c9cad783c.avif?t=1763846019\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras_big/b3461cecee9bb60fa4f1133c9cad783c.webp?t=1763846019 width=1560 height=306 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中专精于不同的魔法流派。毕业时，属性点的不同组合将为你开启30余种结局中的其中一种。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/c275c3990b7e0acfecaa4eac0f4d8da6.poster.avif?t=1763846019\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/c275c3990b7e0acfecaa4eac0f4d8da6.webm?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377250/extras/c275c3990b7e0acfecaa4eac0f4d8da6.mp4?t=1763846019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
